      <div class="SOTTO_PARA"><a name="DUCe0bfc2802b87100583ae89ec0e3196d2"></a>Removing the footpegs
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="titoleto"><a name="d3e8619"> </a>Removing the front footpegs
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="SOTTO_PARA">
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8622"> </a>Remove the circlip (1) thereby releasing the pin (2).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8624"> </a>Slide out pin (2), while supporting the footpeg (3).
         </div>
         <div class="Testo"><a name="d3e8626"> </a>Slide out footpeg (3) from its seat and collect spring (4).
         </div>
      </div>
      <div class="AggancioFigure">
         <center><img class="Default" src="img/DUC_MO_MTS1200_7_031603450.jpg"></center>
      </div>
